## President's Report

Bdale reported that there had been a well-attended SPI BOF during DebConf11 in
Banja Luka. A video recording of the meeting is available at
[http://meetings-archive.debian.net/pub/debian-meetings/2011/debconf11/low/703_SPI_BOF.ogv](http://meetings-archive.debian.net/pub/debian-meetings/2011/debconf11/low/703_SPI_BOF.ogv).
He also congratulated and welcomed our new/returning board members, as well as
thanking David Graham for his many years of service to the board.


